    {
      "id": 72685,
      "is_internal": false,
      "editable": false,
      "type": "Activities::Comment",
      "message": "For this attack, user **need not** have create/edit access to repos. He can have edit access to just one repository.\n\nSimple fix: Might be to disable file:/// protocol\n\nComplicated fix: To use permissions.\n\nI hope you got what I wanted to convey. Btw very quick and awesome response :)",
